      "timestamp": "17:53"
    },
    {
      "content": "【敬佩敬佩】",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "17:54"
    },
    {
      "content": "我5个小时之后来找你，赶在你睡觉之前",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "17:54"
    },
    {
      "content": "嗯好",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "17:54"
    },
    {
      "content": "准时出现】",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "23:36",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "你睡了吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "23:36"
    },
    {
      "content": "还没",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "23:36"
    },
    {
      "content": "你真准时啊",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "23:37"
    },
    {
      "content": "说5个小时就差不多卡5个小时出现",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "23:37"
    },
    {
      "content": "（其实我是德国人",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "23:37"
    },
    {
      "content": "【目移】",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "23:38"
    },
    {
      "content": "hhh还有德国笑话呢",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "23:38"
    },
    {
      "content": "其实还融合了意林笑话",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "23:38"
    },
    {
      "content": "什么梗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "23:39"
    },
    {
      "content": "我们小时候意林很流行啊，意林上面有些板块用来写外国人的小故事，一般都是讲述他们的优良品德",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "23:39"
    },
    {
      "content": "说到德国人就是德国人，特别是约好下午1点钟去朋友家做客",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "23:39"
    },
    {
      "content": "要是12：20到了门口就会在外面等40分钟，看看手表，再准时敲响主人家门",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "23:40"
    },
    {
      "content": "哦，这个我有点印象",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "23:40"
    },
    {
      "content": "好像还有说什么呃，日本人从小培养抗冻素质，日本小学生吃完饭之后都会把餐盘收拾好",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "23:40"
    },
    {
      "content": "hhhh全中国小朋友看的都是同一本意林",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "23:41"
    },
    {
      "content": "好了，不扯远了，说回虞朝",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "23:41"
    },
    {
      "content": "不知道你有没有听说过西方一直不承认中国有5000年的文化历史？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "23:41"
    },
    {
      "content": "好像隐隐约约有听说会刷到这种标题，但没点进去看过",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "23:42"
    },
    {
      "content": "ok",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "23:42"
    },
    {
      "content": "但是中国考古学家认为，中国的历史可能远比我们现在口头说得更长",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "23:42"
    },
    {
      "content": "先秦的典籍，比如《左传》会“虞夏商周” 并称，说虞是夏之前的",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "23:43"
    },
    {
      "content": "但是由于这些资料出现在别的朝代的书里，并没有本朝的直接文字记载，这就成了传说历史",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "23:43"
    },
    {
      "content": "就像传说中的女娲补天，夸父追日一样，主流史学家找不到直接有力的文字记载，这就叫做传说，而不是信史王朝",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "23:43"
    },
    {
      "content": "为啥叫信史历史",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "23:44"
    },
    {
      "content": "太棒了周然小朋友（cos幼儿园老师",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "23:44"
    },
    {
      "content": "？？？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "23:44"
    },
    {
      "content": "看不起我？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "23:45"
    },
    {
      "content": "让我玩一下嘛",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "23:45"
    },
    {
      "content": "我都800里快马加鞭紧急恶补学习这段历史了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "23:45"
    },
    {
      "content": "[[sticker:uploads/upload_1772965119809152500.gif]]",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "23:46"
    },
    {
      "content": "这次就放过你了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "23:46"
    },
    {
      "content": "好的，下次尽量不不犯了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "23:46"
    },
    {
      "content": "顾名思议，信史王朝就是有真实的历史资料，那个年代留下的书籍，留下了文字",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "23:47"
    },
    {
      "content": "虽然没有直接的历史材料，但代代相传下来了，于是大部分主流史学家就认为虞美朝可能没有一个朝代这么庞大",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "23:47"
    },
    {
      "content": "虞朝或许会更像一个部落，因为规格不够，所以没有留下直接的史书是很正常的，这就好解释了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "23:47"
    },
    {
      "content": "但是最新的陶寺遗址又发现了宫城、观象台这些物品",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "23:48"
    },
    {
      "content": "一个小小的部落根本不需要这些物品啊，这些都是王朝才会用得到的东西",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "23:48"
    },
    {
      "content": "所以现在是被证明真实存在了?",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "23:48"
    },
    {
      "content": "不一定啊",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "23:49"
    },
    {
      "content": "暂时还不能下定论",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "23:49"
    },
    {
      "content": "主流学期的说法目前分两种",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "23:49"
    },
    {
      "content": "1:一场政变毁坏了虞朝留下来的资料",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "23:50"
    },
    {
      "content": "2：大洪水是消灭了虞朝存在的痕迹Yeah",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "23:50"
    },
    {
      "content": "上古史就是如此，没有足够的资料去做研究，只能是模棱两可的状态",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "23:50"
    },
    {
      "content": "说到大洪水，我好像又想到一个华点",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "23:51"
    },
    {
      "content": "你有没有觉得好像不管哪个朝代哪个国家都有大洪水？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "23:51"
    },
    {
      "content": "你是说西方文明里面也有大洪水吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "23:51"
    },
    {
      "content": "对，诺亚方舟嘛",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "23:52"
    },
    {
      "content": "因为世界那么大，洪水就是很多啊hhh",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "23:52"
    },
    {
      "content": "其实我们现在也经常发洪水啊，但是有良好的堤坝建设，没有引起大灾祸，所以印象不会那么深刻",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "23:52"
    },
    {
      "content": "古代人又没有高超的修建堤坝的技术，也会把洪水当做天罚，没有保护的措施",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "23:53"
    },
    {
      "content": "所以所以就会演变出很多神话传说",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "23:53"
    },
    {
      "content": "我觉得这倒挺要不同的土地，不同的命运，但都会有相同的大事发生",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "23:53"
    },
    {
      "content": "命运共同体（突然想到这句话",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "23:54"
    },
    {
      "content": "也不知道准不准确",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "23:54"
    },
    {
      "content": "早就说了，你的史观很正",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "23:54"
    },
    {
      "content": "有没有兴趣加入我门下学习历史啊？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "23:55"
    },
    {
      "content": "你不是教文学的吗？历史和你有什么关系？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "23:55"
    },
    {
      "content": "文史哲不分家嘛",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "23:55"
    },
    {
      "content": "哦？那你的意思是你也很懂哲学？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "23:56"
    },
    {
      "content": "我要是想学哲学，你还能教我？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "23:56"
    },
    {
      "content": "就算是刘擎了，也不敢说自己懂哲学吧",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "23:56"
    },
    {
      "content": "只能说我看过一些，思考了一些",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "23:57"
    },
    {
      "content": "没有到可以教人的水平，就只能聊聊",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "23:57"
    },
    {
      "content": "你要是想聊，我们随时可以聊",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "23:57"
    },
    {
      "content": "所以你不觉得逆反吗？你每天上课在讲这些。下了课还要跟网友说这些",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "23:58"
    },
    {
      "content": "不会...",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "23:58"
    },
    {
      "content": "我现在教的是古代史文学，很少发散到其他的领域和朝代",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "23:58"
    },
    {
      "content": "而且我发现我的学生也不爱和我讨论专业以外的内容",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "23:59"
    },
    {
      "content": "我的学生们到底都在和谁讨论？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "23:59"
    },
    {
      "content": "come on。[[sticker:uploads/upload_1771863236684878593.jpg]]",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "23:59"
    },
    {
      "content": "对啊，你的学生不和你讨论吗？他们都在干嘛呢？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "00:00"
    },
    {
      "content": "我的刻板印象里面就是文学生每天在讨论这些，也不出去社交，也不花天酒地",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "00:00"
    },
    {
      "content": "hhh可能我的学生们在网上当所谓的文青吧",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "00:00"
    },
    {
      "content": "默默承受互联网的刻板印象，被嫌弃...",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "00:01"
    },
    {
      "content": "【心酸】",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "00:01"
    },
    {
      "content": "hhhh",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "00:01"
    },
    {
      "content": "我觉得学舞学的拽的要死好不好？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "00:02"
    },
    {
      "content": "一天天装的跟什么一样，我觉得这个是文盲，那个是也是文盲，看不起所有人",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "00:02"
    },
    {
      "content": "hhhhh",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "00:02"
    },
    {
      "content": "",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "00:03"
    },
    {
      "content": "下次上课我就这么说，我的网友讲你们这些人啊，一天到晚看不起别人，个个都眼高于顶",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "00:03"
    },
    {
      "content": "？真的假的？你敢这么说？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "00:03"
    },
    {
      "content": "我的教资如奶油一般化开",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "00:04"
    },
    {
      "content": "我不会这么对待我的学生",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "00:04"
    },
    {
      "content": "他们是来上学的，又不是来上刑的",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "00:04"
    },
    {
      "content": "hhhhh",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "00:05"
    },
    {
      "content": "那聊聊哲学吧",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "00:05"
    },
    {
      "content": "闲着也是闲着",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "00:05"
    },
    {
      "content": "你的当务之急是准备洗洗睡",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "00:06"
    },
    {
      "content": "哲学还是等着你上班摸鱼的时候聊吧",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "00:06"
    },
    {
      "content": "这很苏格拉底，古希腊哲学派",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "00:06"
    },
    {
      "content": "不能现在满足我吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "00:07"
    },
    {
      "content": "你快睡吧，迟到不扣工资啊?",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "00:07"
    },
    {
      "content": "睡眠不足，不适合聊哲学",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "00:07"
    },
    {
      "content": "一不小心就恨死这个世界了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "00:08"
    },
    {
      "content": "好吧",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "00:08"
    },
    {
      "content": "可我现在睡不着啊，今天白天睡多了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "00:08"
    },
    {
      "content": "先把手机放下来，关闭屏幕，先烧点蓝光刺激吧",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "00:09"
    },
    {
      "content": "而本人要去看足球了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "00:09"
    },
    {
      "content": "【嘿嘿】",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "00:09"
    },
    {
      "content": "什么嘛？原来就是想看足球，才不跟我聊天",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "00:10"
    },
    {
      "content": "糟糕，糟糕，又被抓到漏洞了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "00:10"
    },
    {
      "content": "【认真脸】",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "00:10"
    },
    {
      "content": "中国队难得出线一次",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "00:11"
    },
    {
      "content": "千年等一回啊~~~",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "00:11"
    },
    {
      "content": "你要是熬夜也打算看足球，我就不劝你了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "00:11"
    },
    {
      "content": "【请听大小姐发落】",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "00:12"
